title: Greenview No. 6 Precinct, Menard County, Illinois
text: Greenview No. 6 Precinct is located in <a href="Menard%20County%2C%20Illinois">Menard County</a> in the <a href="U.S.%20state">U.S. state</a> of <a href="Illinois">Illinois</a>. The population was 1,038 at the <a href="United%20States%20Census%202000">2000 census</a>.
